star.idres.lookup

Interface EnrichmentService

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Service

    public interface EnrichmentService
extends Service
    Defines requests that perform the enrichment of position report messages. It will be invoked for each position message in the stream so that it will need to respond very quickly. For this reason the data set is replicated in the client process memory. It only contains the most recent values for those attributes that are changing regularly in order to keep the size of the data set limited. It is therefore assumed that the positions being enriched are quite recent.
